a Illustration of the device and mechanism of electrocatalytic water-splitting. b Overview of the representative elements constituting the water-splitting catalyst and the current anion-mixed pairs
Large number of surface-active sites.
High electronic conductivity.
High intrinsic activity.
Suitable specific adsorption/desorption energy of the intermediate species.
